description.en:
All Time High — experimental ERC20 algorithmic token with constant growth formula

Huge growth potential
A sustainable new tokenomics model
Fomo chart
Hodlers wins

These are the things we’ve been missing for so long in crypto space… So the idea of creating a new conceptually different token was born.
